<br>
One of the sages talks about finding items and extracting the magical energies that bind the spells to the item.<br>
<br>
One theory is the 61+ spells, inserted into the box, hit combine, will create a blank parchment and &quot;magical binding&quot;, which combined with other pieces of the quest, create a new parchment which you can then turn in for a spell.<br>
<br>
However, I have no spells at all, and certainly no extras.  So perhaps somebody with an extra &quot;summon choker&quot; or not so useful spell can make the attempt.  Odds are nothing will happen, but I'd like to make sure.<br>
<br>
Please post here if you attempted this.<br>
<br>
